title: Terror attack foiled in Dera Murad Jamali - Pakistan - DAWN.COM
content:
DERA MURAD JAMALI: Nasirabad police foiled an attempt of terror attack in Dera Murad Jamali and seized a huge quantity of explosives dumped underground in White Choki area.

SSP Nasirabad Ghulam Sarwar told a press conference on Sunday that a team of police officers raided the White Choki area seized 14kg of explosives dumped underground.

Published in Dawn, April 14th, 2025
